{"tid":1816360,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"第二屆人像風景攝影大賽","createTime":"2020-01-08T07:49:14.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-08T07:50:34.000Z","uid":223933,"like":7,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"ca70b5e1272af3ac8cc287f0e4e679be984122a1","tid":1816360,"uid":223933,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-08T07:49:14.000Z","msg":"大家好 又係本聖<br />\n<br />\n有鑑於連日嚟警察嘅濫捕，<br />\n不擇手段想嚇怕我哋和理非。<br />\n<br />\n所以本聖現正參考此舉，並大範圍、無定向 濫攝人像同風景並呼籲各方人士加入此項盛事。<br />\n<br />\n比賽現在開始<br />\n結束時間為警方立即停止濫捕行為之後<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n為打響頭炮<br />\n<br />\n本聖私人贈送兩張美人美景供大家欣賞，並在稍後日子每天發放一張供各位參賽者借鑑，務求令到各參賽者拍到一張心滿意足的照片。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/EHnEgp9.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FEHnEgp9.png&h=35d1f9ad&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/mYckLiz.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FmYckLiz.png&h=f8f48c20&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"45e90e4530db320f94c09365f3c0fd3475e97f77","tid":1816360,"uid":223933,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-08T07:50:34.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/dZODwZJ.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FdZODwZJ.png&h=e1552463&s={SIZE}\" />"}]}